OL,3,CWeather warning in place as strong
OL,4,Cwinds cause disruption
OL,6,FA weather warning is in place in
OL,7,FCumbria and southern Scotland as
OL,8,Fstrong winds and rain cause disruption.
OL,10,FA road was blocked by a fallen tree in
OL,11,Fa Lake District village, as winds of
OL,12,Fup to 70mph have been felt amidst the
OL,13,FMet Office alert.
OL,15,FThe tree was blown over in Stair,
OL,16,Fclose to Keswick, according to the
OL,17,FCumbria Road Watch social media page.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
