OL,3,CWeather warning in place as strong
OL,4,Cwinds cause disruption
OL,6,FThe yellow Met Office weather warning
OL,7,Ffor wind will remain in place until
OL,8,F8pm on Thursday, with gusts from the
OL,9,Fnorth set to ease later in the day.
OL,11,FPart of the A66 is shut to high-sided
OL,12,Fvehicles and the A5093 in South
OL,13,FCumbria is currently closed due to
OL,14,Ffallen power cables.
OL,16,FWhat should you expect from the
OL,17,Fweather warning?
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
